WEBVTT

00:01:36.460 --> 00:01:41.059 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:01:41.160 --> 00:01:43.730 line:80%
[Episode 27]

00:02:04.540 --> 00:02:05.200 line:80%
Be careful!

00:02:10.900 --> 00:02:11.460 line:80%
Changyu,

00:02:12.290 --> 00:02:13.380 line:80%
let me explain.

00:02:13.610 --> 00:02:14.610 line:80%
You lied to me.

00:02:14.950 --> 00:02:16.280 line:80%
You lied to me in Lin'an.

00:02:16.690 --> 00:02:18.160 line:80%
And you lied to me in the camp.

00:02:18.160 --> 00:02:19.960 line:80%
You've been lying to me all along!

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:21.360 line:80%
Is this injury also fake?

00:02:23.710 --> 00:02:24.870 line:80%
Did you get hurt?

00:02:25.620 --> 00:02:27.280 line:80%
This is none of your business.

00:02:28.710 --> 00:02:29.990 line:80%
About what you just said,

00:02:29.990 --> 00:02:31.450 line:80%
I can explain everything.

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:34.930 line:80%
Come back with me to get treated first.

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:37.530 line:80%
I am just a butcher's daughter.

00:02:37.890 --> 00:02:41.550 line:80%
How could I let the grand Marquis of Wu'an
trouble himself with me?

00:02:43.450 --> 00:02:46.010 line:80%
You want me
to stay out of your business, right?

00:02:46.010 --> 00:02:48.379 line:80%
Then why did you drug me
and go to the battlefield?

00:02:48.379 --> 00:02:50.140 line:80%
Do you know what a battlefield is?

00:02:50.140 --> 00:02:52.870 line:80%
It's a place
where human lives are worth nothing!

00:02:53.220 --> 00:02:54.550 line:80%
Did you forget everything I told you

00:02:54.550 --> 00:02:56.140 line:80%
when you snatched the sheep and salt?

00:02:56.140 --> 00:02:58.140 line:80%
When we snatched the sheep and salt,

00:02:58.540 --> 00:03:00.670 line:80%
you were also lying to me, weren't you?

00:03:01.340 --> 00:03:02.380 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an,

00:03:02.650 --> 00:03:04.150 line:80%
was it fun deceiving me?

00:03:04.740 --> 00:03:06.140 line:80%
I went to the battlefield

00:03:06.470 --> 00:03:08.150 line:80%
because you lied to me!

00:03:08.710 --> 00:03:09.740 line:80%
I drugged you

00:03:09.930 --> 00:03:12.730 line:80%
because I was afraid
you'd die on the battlefield!

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:22.560 line:80%
I can die,

00:03:23.020 --> 00:03:24.950 line:80%
but you must survive and live well!

00:03:33.790 --> 00:03:35.010 line:80%
If I die,

00:03:36.710 --> 00:03:38.440 line:80%
you can take Fan Changning away

00:03:38.750 --> 00:03:40.680 line:80%
and find somewhere to settle down.

00:03:42.129 --> 00:03:43.950 line:80%
You can either open a braised meat shop

00:03:43.950 --> 00:03:45.650 line:80%
or build a sty to raise pigs.

00:03:45.780 --> 00:03:47.110 line:80%
As long as you're alive,

00:03:47.530 --> 00:03:49.129 line:80%
you can do whatever you want.

00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:57.180 line:80%
Find a gentle scholar
you like in the future

00:03:57.180 --> 00:03:58.379 line:80%
and bear children...

00:03:59.310 --> 00:04:00.910 line:80%
I won't be able to intervene.

00:04:49.170 --> 00:04:50.880 line:80%
But as long as I'm alive,

00:04:52.130 --> 00:04:53.130 line:80%
you will

00:04:54.130 --> 00:04:55.340 line:80%
always be mine.

00:05:17.020 --> 00:05:17.620 line:80%
Hyah!

00:05:19.750 --> 00:05:20.350 line:80%
Hyah!

00:05:21.060 --> 00:05:21.620 line:80%
My Lady,

00:05:21.810 --> 00:05:24.070 line:80%
your friend Mandi is seriously injured.

00:05:24.580 --> 00:05:25.260 line:80%
Where is he?

00:05:25.260 --> 00:05:26.780 line:80%
Jin Yuanbao took him back to the camp.

00:05:26.780 --> 00:05:28.180 line:80%
My Lady, your headscarf.

00:05:28.750 --> 00:05:29.360 line:80%
Hyah!

00:05:32.990 --> 00:05:33.380 line:80%
Hyah!

00:05:33.380 --> 00:05:34.020 line:80%
My Lord,

00:05:34.230 --> 00:05:35.690 line:80%
the Counselor is wounded!

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:38.300 line:80%
Please wake up.

00:05:38.870 --> 00:05:41.580 line:80%
You've been with us since you were a teen.

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:43.770 line:80%
If you leave without a word,

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:46.800 line:80%
how am I supposed to explain it
to your younger sister?

00:05:50.990 --> 00:05:52.320 line:80%
What happened to Mandi?

00:05:53.190 --> 00:05:55.140 line:80%
He was stabbed right through the chest.

00:05:55.140 --> 00:05:56.670 line:80%
Blood has been gushing out.

00:05:57.140 --> 00:05:58.940 line:80%
The medic lady was here just now.

00:05:59.350 --> 00:05:59.940 line:80%
She shook her head

00:05:59.940 --> 00:06:01.670 line:80%
and left without saying a word.

00:06:03.060 --> 00:06:04.400 line:80%
How could this happen?

00:06:04.990 --> 00:06:08.020 line:80%
When we were cleaning up the battlefield,

00:06:08.550 --> 00:06:09.750 line:80%
somehow,

00:06:10.430 --> 00:06:12.450 line:80%
from a pile of dead bodies,

00:06:12.710 --> 00:06:14.840 line:80%
a little soldier suddenly rushed out.

00:06:25.330 --> 00:06:26.490 line:80%
-Mandi!
-Mandi!

00:06:34.580 --> 00:06:35.470 line:80%
Are you talking

00:06:35.580 --> 00:06:37.780 line:80%
about the boy who guarded the catapult?

00:06:38.070 --> 00:06:39.300 line:80%
It was him!

00:06:44.390 --> 00:06:46.590 line:80%
I shouldn't have been so soft-hearted.

00:06:47.950 --> 00:06:49.870 line:80%
If I had killed that kid back then,

00:06:51.170 --> 00:06:53.370 line:80%
Mandi wouldn't be lying here like this.

00:06:57.820 --> 00:06:59.430 line:80%
Didn't I say no crowding?

00:07:00.230 --> 00:07:01.030 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:07:01.260 --> 00:07:02.120 line:80%
Miss Beholden,

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:03.200 line:80%
please save him.

00:07:03.870 --> 00:07:05.870 line:80%
Don't worry. It's nothing serious.

00:07:06.260 --> 00:07:07.500 line:80%
Nothing serious?

00:07:07.530 --> 00:07:08.430 line:80%
I just heard you say

00:07:08.430 --> 00:07:10.290 line:80%
he was stabbed through the chest!

00:07:11.140 --> 00:07:13.870 line:80%
It was his breastplate
that got stabbed through.

00:07:14.990 --> 00:07:16.350 line:80%
Thankfully, it prevented the blow

00:07:16.350 --> 00:07:18.350 line:80%
from damaging his internal organs.

00:07:19.430 --> 00:07:20.630 line:80%
This breastplate was

00:07:21.550 --> 00:07:23.950 line:80%
what Mandi's sister asked me
to give to him.

00:07:25.580 --> 00:07:26.990 line:80%
When I was cleaning his wound,

00:07:26.990 --> 00:07:28.550 line:80%
you grown men

00:07:28.580 --> 00:07:29.670 line:80%
all covered your faces,

00:07:29.670 --> 00:07:30.730 line:80%
too scared to look.

00:07:31.320 --> 00:07:33.320 line:80%
And now you're scaring yourselves.

00:07:33.850 --> 00:07:34.750 line:80%
What about his face?

00:07:34.750 --> 00:07:35.610 line:80%
A-And his lips?

00:07:35.620 --> 00:07:37.430 line:80%
He's even paler
than a corpse dead for 3 days.

00:07:37.430 --> 00:07:39.090 line:80%
That's from excessive shock.

00:07:39.390 --> 00:07:40.620 line:80%
He's already frail.

00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:43.459 line:80%
That's why I told you
not to crowd around him.

00:07:43.459 --> 00:07:44.580 line:80%
Let him rest well.

00:07:45.010 --> 00:07:46.040 line:80%
He's fine!

00:07:46.070 --> 00:07:47.270 line:80%
I'll get back to work.

00:07:47.490 --> 00:07:48.200 line:80%
Thank you.

00:07:50.260 --> 00:07:51.320 line:80%
That's great news.

00:07:52.260 --> 00:07:53.310 line:80%
He's fine, Big Brother.

00:07:53.310 --> 00:07:54.190 line:80%
I'm glad to hear

00:07:54.420 --> 00:07:55.280 line:80%
that he's okay.

00:08:09.700 --> 00:08:10.350 line:80%
Pull.

00:08:19.500 --> 00:08:19.990 line:80%
Report!

00:08:20.260 --> 00:08:21.910 line:80%
General Shi Hu was killed
by a female soldier

00:08:21.910 --> 00:08:24.310 line:80%
with a butcher knife
from the enemy forces!

00:08:26.310 --> 00:08:27.240 line:80%
What did you say?

00:08:27.430 --> 00:08:29.070 line:80%
The General was killed
by a female soldier.

00:08:29.070 --> 00:08:30.070 line:80%
Hu?

00:08:33.370 --> 00:08:34.280 line:80%
Impossible.

00:08:35.109 --> 00:08:37.450 line:80%
Hu has the unmatched prowess,
even against 10,000 men.

00:08:37.450 --> 00:08:40.870 line:80%
General Shi Hu has the unmatched prowess,
even against 10,000 men!

00:08:40.870 --> 00:08:42.150 line:80%
I saw it with my own eyes.

00:08:42.150 --> 00:08:43.810 line:80%
General Shi Hu's Golden Melon Mace was
snatched away.

00:08:43.810 --> 00:08:44.560 line:80%
Three hits.

00:08:44.710 --> 00:08:45.260 line:80%
No,

00:08:45.380 --> 00:08:47.110 line:80%
he was beaten to death by 2 hits!

00:08:49.510 --> 00:08:51.090 line:80%
I said it's impossible.

00:08:52.020 --> 00:08:52.830 line:80%
Scout again!

00:08:52.850 --> 00:08:53.520 line:80%
Yes, sir!

00:08:54.770 --> 00:08:55.480 line:80%
No.

00:08:58.300 --> 00:09:00.780 line:80%
That person must be Fan Changyu.

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:05.940 line:80%
Fan Changyu?

00:09:06.680 --> 00:09:07.200 line:80%
Report!

00:09:07.220 --> 00:09:08.370 line:80%
The Yanzhou Army and Jizhou Army

00:09:08.370 --> 00:09:09.800 line:80%
gathered in the southwest
and marched here.

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:11.190 line:80%
They are joining forces to besiege us.

00:09:11.190 --> 00:09:13.650 line:80%
Our troops are now under attack
from 3 sides.

00:09:14.610 --> 00:09:15.820 line:80%
Let's set off.

00:09:17.540 --> 00:09:19.800 line:80%
Father is waiting for us in Lucheng.

00:09:19.820 --> 00:09:21.030 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:09:21.250 --> 00:09:23.090 line:80%
I said, withdraw.

00:09:30.700 --> 00:09:32.480 line:80%
You're right, Your Highness.

00:09:32.890 --> 00:09:34.290 line:80%
The Prince's great cause

00:09:35.800 --> 00:09:36.800 line:80%
cannot wait.

00:09:38.420 --> 00:09:39.540 line:80%
Retreat!

00:09:42.540 --> 00:09:45.140 line:80%
I led men to block them desperately
on the battlefield,

00:09:45.140 --> 00:09:46.870 line:80%
yet I still failed to stop them.

00:09:47.110 --> 00:09:48.840 line:80%
Shi Yue took Sui Yuanqing away,

00:09:48.840 --> 00:09:50.240 line:80%
and I got myself injured.

00:09:52.450 --> 00:09:55.180 line:80%
Scholars really are useless
on the battlefield.

00:09:55.280 --> 00:09:57.040 line:80%
I told you to wear armor,
but you didn't listen.

00:09:57.040 --> 00:09:58.600 line:80%
You insisted on imitating Zhuge Liang.

00:09:58.600 --> 00:10:00.000 line:80%
Do you even look like him?

00:10:02.400 --> 00:10:03.160 line:80%
Xie Jiu,

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:06.040 line:80%
go to the Yanzhou Army's camp
and invite Medic Lu over.

00:10:06.040 --> 00:10:06.570 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:10:07.430 --> 00:10:08.030 line:80%
Come back.

00:10:11.910 --> 00:10:13.550 line:80%
My injury is minor,

00:10:13.780 --> 00:10:15.690 line:80%
not enough to trouble a medic.

00:10:15.720 --> 00:10:17.920 line:80%
Don't use a sledgehammer to crack a nut.

00:10:19.170 --> 00:10:20.230 line:80%
Minor injury, huh?

00:10:21.230 --> 00:10:21.710 line:80%
Fine.

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:23.160 line:80%
Fetch the vet here.

00:10:23.400 --> 00:10:24.000 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:10:24.830 --> 00:10:25.430 line:80%
Come back!

00:10:26.610 --> 00:10:29.900 line:80%
Do we have no other physicians here?

00:10:33.300 --> 00:10:33.950 line:80%
How about

00:10:34.630 --> 00:10:36.070 line:80%
I invite the Princess Royal over

00:10:36.070 --> 00:10:37.070 line:80%
to check in on you?

00:10:40.070 --> 00:10:41.330 line:80%
Go tell Her Highness

00:10:41.750 --> 00:10:43.340 line:80%
that I'm gravely injured,

00:10:43.370 --> 00:10:44.990 line:80%
and my life is in danger.

00:10:45.420 --> 00:10:48.020 line:80%
But you don't look like it, sir.

00:10:48.260 --> 00:10:50.590 line:80%
Of course you can't tell from the outside.

00:10:50.840 --> 00:10:52.840 line:80%
It's actually all messed up inside.

00:10:54.200 --> 00:10:54.800 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:10:57.380 --> 00:10:58.500 line:80%
I have urgent matters to handle.

00:10:58.500 --> 00:10:59.560 line:80%
I'll take my leave.

00:11:21.140 --> 00:11:22.070 line:80%
Little Gongsun,

00:11:22.070 --> 00:11:23.550 line:80%
I heard about your fatal injuries.

00:11:23.550 --> 00:11:26.470 line:80%
I came specifically to chant sutras
for your final journey.

00:11:26.470 --> 00:11:28.110 line:80%
Om mani padme hum.

00:11:28.180 --> 00:11:29.450 line:80%
Om mani padme hum.

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:33.440 line:80%
Om mani padme hum.

00:11:33.460 --> 00:11:34.810 line:80%
Om mani padme hum.

00:11:35.060 --> 00:11:36.060 line:80%
Stop it.

00:11:37.190 --> 00:11:40.050 line:80%
If you keep chanting,
you'll actually send me away.

00:11:48.660 --> 00:11:49.870 line:80%
Little Gongsun,

00:11:50.260 --> 00:11:52.970 line:80%
you've endured trials along the way.
Thank you for everything.

00:11:52.970 --> 00:11:54.110 line:80%
It's nothing.

00:11:54.850 --> 00:11:56.540 line:80%
His Lordship cares for the world.

00:11:56.540 --> 00:11:58.050 line:80%
I admire him greatly.

00:11:58.420 --> 00:12:00.350 line:80%
I'm willing
to go through thick and thin with him.

00:12:00.350 --> 00:12:01.620 line:80%
It's really nothing.

00:12:02.860 --> 00:12:05.610 line:80%
During the confrontation
with the Chongzhou Army,

00:12:05.610 --> 00:12:08.200 line:80%
His Lordship
made a narrow escape, fortunately.

00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:10.580 line:80%
Grand Tutor, you really
don't need to worry about him too much.

00:12:10.580 --> 00:12:13.580 line:80%
I won't be worried
about that bratty disciple of mine.

00:12:14.090 --> 00:12:15.190 line:80%
Half a month ago,

00:12:15.220 --> 00:12:18.470 line:80%
in the Jizhou Army
delivering supplies up the mountain,

00:12:18.500 --> 00:12:20.830 line:80%
there was someone whom I consider
half my disciple.

00:12:20.830 --> 00:12:22.380 line:80%
She rashly went up the mountain
to deliver supplies

00:12:22.380 --> 00:12:23.780 line:80%
and never came down.

00:12:23.780 --> 00:12:26.380 line:80%
I don't know how she is doing right now.

00:12:26.410 --> 00:12:28.330 line:80%
A soldier delivering supplies?

00:12:28.670 --> 00:12:29.370 line:80%
Yes.

00:12:29.530 --> 00:12:30.930 line:80%
And she's your disciple?

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:31.680 line:80%
Yes.

00:12:31.920 --> 00:12:33.120 line:80%
But as far as I know,

00:12:33.190 --> 00:12:36.590 line:80%
your standards for accepting disciples are
extremely high.

00:12:36.730 --> 00:12:38.330 line:80%
Across the entire Great Yin,

00:12:38.350 --> 00:12:40.700 line:80%
only Jiuheng caught your eye.

00:12:40.730 --> 00:12:42.700 line:80%
How could a random soldier on the road

00:12:42.700 --> 00:12:44.140 line:80%
win your favor?

00:12:44.170 --> 00:12:45.990 line:80%
And why is she half your disciple?

00:12:45.990 --> 00:12:48.060 line:80%
That girl is amazingly brawny

00:12:48.080 --> 00:12:51.770 line:80%
as a rare martial arts prodigy,

00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:55.000 line:80%
but she's just a bit less brainy.

00:12:55.020 --> 00:12:56.230 line:80%
She doesn't like to read.

00:12:56.230 --> 00:12:57.190 line:80%
So I

00:12:57.190 --> 00:12:59.110 line:80%
see her as half a disciple

00:12:59.300 --> 00:13:00.470 line:80%
of mine.

00:13:01.910 --> 00:13:03.060 line:80%
Girl?

00:13:03.730 --> 00:13:05.590 line:80%
Your Highness, please slow down!

00:13:05.950 --> 00:13:07.080 line:80%
Be careful, please!

00:13:08.900 --> 00:13:10.700 line:80%
Your Highness, are you alright?

00:13:16.500 --> 00:13:18.360 line:80%
Your Highness, this is improper.

00:13:18.380 --> 00:13:19.870 line:80%
Xie Jiu said he's dying.

00:13:19.900 --> 00:13:20.750 line:80%
Who cares about propriety?

00:13:20.750 --> 00:13:21.590 line:80%
Wait for me.

00:13:22.420 --> 00:13:23.300 line:80%
Grand Tutor,

00:13:24.250 --> 00:13:27.490 line:80%
is this disciple you mentioned named Fan?

00:13:28.780 --> 00:13:30.050 line:80%
Her surname is indeed Fan.

00:13:30.050 --> 00:13:31.030 line:80%
And her given name is Changyu.

00:13:31.030 --> 00:13:32.500 line:80%
She's 19.

00:13:32.710 --> 00:13:35.280 line:80%
What? Little Gongsun, you know her?

00:13:36.080 --> 00:13:38.880 line:80%
-Does my bratty disciple know her then?
-Gongsun!

00:13:45.960 --> 00:13:48.690 line:80%
Is this what Xie Jiu meant
by saying you're dying?

00:13:49.950 --> 00:13:50.920 line:80%
I am dying.

00:13:51.280 --> 00:13:52.740 line:80%
It's all messed up inside.

00:13:53.950 --> 00:13:56.880 line:80%
Your Highness, my greetings!

00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:57.820 line:80%
Your Highness!

00:13:58.840 --> 00:13:59.740 line:80%
Excuse me.

00:14:00.490 --> 00:14:01.350 line:80%
Your Highness!

00:14:01.740 --> 00:14:03.470 line:80%
Your Highness, let me explain.

00:14:03.500 --> 00:14:04.290 line:80%
Your Highness!

00:14:04.290 --> 00:14:05.720 line:80%
Your Highness, be careful. Your Highness!

00:14:05.720 --> 00:14:06.830 line:80%
Please listen to me.

00:14:06.830 --> 00:14:07.970 line:80%
Your Highness, please hear me out.

00:14:07.970 --> 00:14:09.760 line:80%
Why did you trick me, Headmaster?

00:14:09.760 --> 00:14:11.620 line:80%
I didn't mean to trick you. I was...

00:14:11.620 --> 00:14:12.450 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:14:14.420 --> 00:14:15.060 line:80%
I...

00:14:16.470 --> 00:14:17.830 line:80%
I just didn't expect you

00:14:18.660 --> 00:14:21.320 line:80%
to come to visit me so anxiously,
Your Highness.

00:14:21.350 --> 00:14:21.900 line:80%
So...

00:14:29.420 --> 00:14:30.950 line:80%
Don't bother taking it off.

00:14:31.600 --> 00:14:32.400 line:80%
It's too late.

00:14:36.260 --> 00:14:37.640 line:80%
Pardon my impropriety.

00:14:37.990 --> 00:14:39.190 line:80%
I just remember

00:14:39.620 --> 00:14:41.950 line:80%
you encouraged me
when we were going out to battle...

00:14:41.950 --> 00:14:42.680 line:80%
Headmaster.

00:14:43.750 --> 00:14:45.070 line:80%
What I said this morning was

00:14:45.070 --> 00:14:47.200 line:80%
just to boost the morale of the troops.

00:14:47.270 --> 00:14:48.400 line:80%
Don't overthink it.

00:14:51.650 --> 00:14:53.640 line:80%
It seems you are fine, Headmaster.

00:14:54.030 --> 00:14:56.430 line:80%
I still have
other wounded people to treat.

00:14:56.930 --> 00:14:58.450 line:80%
I'll take my leave.

00:15:01.740 --> 00:15:02.730 line:80%
Your Highness, does it hurt?

00:15:02.730 --> 00:15:04.380 line:80%
It hurts, but I can endure it.

00:15:18.100 --> 00:15:18.860 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:15:19.720 --> 00:15:21.520 line:80%
The Mess Crew made ginger soup
to ward off the cold.

00:15:21.520 --> 00:15:22.650 line:80%
I brought you a bowl.

00:15:23.430 --> 00:15:25.360 line:80%
Don't bother, General Jiu.

00:15:25.380 --> 00:15:27.110 line:80%
Please give it to someone else.

00:15:41.190 --> 00:15:42.520 line:80%
Is there anything else?

00:16:01.710 --> 00:16:02.970 line:80%
I didn't mean to hide it

00:16:03.570 --> 00:16:04.660 line:80%
from you back then.

00:16:05.050 --> 00:16:06.450 line:80%
I was set up,

00:16:07.150 --> 00:16:08.150 line:80%
hunted down,

00:16:09.150 --> 00:16:10.480 line:80%
and stranded in Lin'an.

00:16:11.990 --> 00:16:14.090 line:80%
You happened to save me in the snow.

00:16:14.340 --> 00:16:16.270 line:80%
If I had told you who I was back then,

00:16:16.980 --> 00:16:18.840 line:80%
I feared it would bring disaster.

00:16:19.120 --> 00:16:20.670 line:80%
So I chose to keep it secret.

00:16:22.350 --> 00:16:24.610 line:80%
I don't blame you for hiding it back then.

00:16:26.710 --> 00:16:27.940 line:80%
Then are you blaming me

00:16:27.940 --> 00:16:29.270 line:80%
for hiding it this time?

00:16:40.380 --> 00:16:41.640 line:80%
That you came to find me

00:16:41.660 --> 00:16:42.860 line:80%
made me really happy.

00:16:43.660 --> 00:16:44.750 line:80%
I also knew

00:16:45.190 --> 00:16:46.790 line:80%
that if you learned the truth,

00:16:46.790 --> 00:16:48.520 line:80%
you would be even more furious.

00:16:49.040 --> 00:16:51.560 line:80%
So there were many things
I wanted to explain,

00:16:51.560 --> 00:16:53.240 line:80%
but I couldn't get started.

00:17:01.120 --> 00:17:02.520 line:80%
Changning was kidnapped

00:17:03.590 --> 00:17:05.020 line:80%
because of my identity.

00:17:05.700 --> 00:17:06.770 line:80%
I apologize to you.

00:17:08.570 --> 00:17:10.300 line:80%
I don't blame you for Changning

00:17:11.139 --> 00:17:12.139 line:80%
being kidnapped.

00:17:13.000 --> 00:17:14.790 line:80%
You got hurt trying to save her.

00:17:15.360 --> 00:17:17.020 line:80%
You lied to me on the mountain,

00:17:19.740 --> 00:17:21.800 line:80%
but I don't blame you for that either.

00:17:33.450 --> 00:17:35.250 line:80%
You don't blame me for anything.

00:17:35.420 --> 00:17:36.730 line:80%
Are you trying to say

00:17:36.910 --> 00:17:38.710 line:80%
that you want to split up with me?

00:17:41.190 --> 00:17:42.860 line:80%
We've never been together.

00:17:45.890 --> 00:17:47.530 line:80%
How can we "split up"?

00:17:49.570 --> 00:17:50.570 line:80%
What did you say?

00:17:52.570 --> 00:17:54.760 line:80%
What do you mean
by "we've never been together"?

00:17:54.760 --> 00:17:55.690 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:18:12.190 --> 00:18:13.690 line:80%
We had an agreement.

00:18:16.050 --> 00:18:18.170 line:80%
You pretended to be my matrilocal husband.

00:18:18.170 --> 00:18:21.060 line:80%
But "Yan Zheng" doesn't exist
in this world.

00:18:22.260 --> 00:18:24.060 line:80%
Since Yan Zheng is a fake person,

00:18:26.170 --> 00:18:27.500 line:80%
that marriage contract

00:18:27.520 --> 00:18:28.820 line:80%
should also be fake.

00:18:31.210 --> 00:18:32.940 line:80%
Then why did you come to find me?

00:18:33.670 --> 00:18:35.540 line:80%
Why did you say you'd feed me
by butchering pigs?

00:18:35.540 --> 00:18:36.760 line:80%
Why did you decide
to go to the battlefield

00:18:36.760 --> 00:18:37.570 line:80%
in my place?

00:18:37.590 --> 00:18:39.160 line:80%
I came for Yan Zheng.

00:18:43.260 --> 00:18:44.100 line:80%
Not for Xie Zheng.

00:18:44.100 --> 00:18:45.500 line:80%
Is there any difference?

00:18:46.100 --> 00:18:46.910 line:80%
They're both me.

00:18:46.910 --> 00:18:47.840 line:80%
It is different.

00:18:51.980 --> 00:18:53.420 line:80%
I can't treat you,

00:18:55.710 --> 00:18:57.750 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an, as Yan Zheng.

00:18:59.290 --> 00:19:01.550 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an is an unmatched hero

00:19:01.740 --> 00:19:02.960 line:80%
from a noble house.

00:19:03.210 --> 00:19:05.410 line:80%
If he is together with a female butcher,

00:19:06.420 --> 00:19:08.550 line:80%
everyone in the world will laugh at it.

00:19:18.210 --> 00:19:20.540 line:80%
I have at least that much self-awareness.

00:19:22.580 --> 00:19:24.310 line:80%
I decide who I marry on my own.

00:19:24.780 --> 00:19:26.620 line:80%
What does it have to do with the others?

00:19:26.620 --> 00:19:28.280 line:80%
You are not just a female butcher,

00:19:28.280 --> 00:19:30.240 line:80%
but also a heroine
who made great contributions.

00:19:30.240 --> 00:19:32.440 line:80%
If you really fear the world's mockery,

00:19:32.640 --> 00:19:33.360 line:80%
fine.

00:19:34.530 --> 00:19:36.930 line:80%
I can ask His Majesty
to grant us a marriage.

00:19:37.020 --> 00:19:38.580 line:80%
Then we will be together aboveboard.

00:19:38.580 --> 00:19:40.020 line:80%
Who would dare mock us?

00:20:01.500 --> 00:20:02.260 line:80%
Changyu.

00:20:02.840 --> 00:20:12.980 line:80%
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

00:20:04.020 --> 00:20:05.150 line:80%
My name is Xie Zheng.

00:20:06.140 --> 00:20:07.740 line:80%
My courtesy name is Jiuheng.

00:20:09.030 --> 00:20:10.500 line:80%
I serve in the army,

00:20:11.150 --> 00:20:12.360 line:80%
and I am from the Capital,

00:20:12.360 --> 00:20:13.630 line:80%
titled Marquis of Wu'an.

00:20:13.630 --> 00:20:23.300 line:80%
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

00:20:16.600 --> 00:20:17.920 line:80%
With a sincere heart,

00:20:19.150 --> 00:20:20.880 line:80%
I ask for your hand in marriage.

00:20:22.870 --> 00:20:24.240 line:80%
May we be together in eternal peace

00:20:24.240 --> 00:20:28.990 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:20:25.120 --> 00:20:27.050 line:80%
and spend our days in tranquility.

00:20:29.010 --> 00:20:33.950 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:20:34.410 --> 00:20:36.760 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:20:37.180 --> 00:20:40.020 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:20:40.780 --> 00:20:45.100 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:20:45.820 --> 00:20:50.120 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:20:50.140 --> 00:20:55.430 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:20:56.050 --> 00:20:58.260 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:20:58.570 --> 00:21:03.160 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:21:04.870 --> 00:21:14.490 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:21:16.330 --> 00:21:17.370 line:80%
I see.

00:21:41.950 --> 00:21:42.670 line:80%
Master?

00:21:47.250 --> 00:21:48.450 line:80%
What brings you here?

00:21:48.580 --> 00:21:51.260 line:80%
Your injury is in a rather tricky spot.

00:21:51.780 --> 00:21:53.190 line:80%
It doesn't look like a wound from battle,

00:21:53.190 --> 00:21:54.020 line:80%
but more like

00:21:54.610 --> 00:21:56.270 line:80%
one from a brawl.

00:21:56.390 --> 00:21:58.520 line:80%
Could it be that you were once again...

00:22:01.860 --> 00:22:03.230 line:80%
In this battle, Lord Changxin

00:22:03.230 --> 00:22:05.100 line:80%
lost a major general, Shi Hu,

00:22:05.670 --> 00:22:06.820 line:80%
but Shi Yue launched a surprise attack

00:22:06.820 --> 00:22:08.280 line:80%
and rescued Sui Yuanqing.

00:22:09.230 --> 00:22:11.230 line:80%
It was due to an oversight in my plan.

00:22:11.630 --> 00:22:14.950 line:80%
The two most capable generals
under Lord Changxin's command are

00:22:14.950 --> 00:22:16.390 line:80%
the Shi brothers.

00:22:16.540 --> 00:22:17.820 line:80%
With Shi Hu dead,

00:22:17.910 --> 00:22:19.840 line:80%
he has lost a right-hand man.

00:22:22.060 --> 00:22:25.780 line:80%
I heard that when you arrived
to support the Yanzhou Army,

00:22:25.780 --> 00:22:27.430 line:80%
Shi Hu was already dead.

00:22:27.430 --> 00:22:30.690 line:80%
Who else in the army could have subdued
such a fierce enemy?

00:22:34.020 --> 00:22:36.070 line:80%
Shi Hu was killed by his wife.

00:22:36.340 --> 00:22:38.090 line:80%
Wife? Whose wife?

00:22:38.910 --> 00:22:39.780 line:80%
His wife?

00:22:39.910 --> 00:22:40.980 line:80%
You're married?

00:22:41.100 --> 00:22:43.630 line:80%
Didn't you say
you'd never marry in your life?

00:22:44.470 --> 00:22:47.120 line:80%
Why didn't you tell me you got married?

00:22:47.670 --> 00:22:48.960 line:80%
It's a long story.

00:22:49.780 --> 00:22:52.300 line:80%
It was a marriage formed
during my time of misfortune.

00:22:52.300 --> 00:22:53.700 line:80%
Your time of misfortune?

00:22:54.860 --> 00:22:56.190 line:80%
I won't ask you anymore.

00:22:56.500 --> 00:22:58.670 line:80%
How did that woman kill Shi Hu?

00:22:59.020 --> 00:23:00.860 line:80%
At that time, we were outnumbered.

00:23:00.860 --> 00:23:02.540 line:80%
The Marchioness grabbed his mace

00:23:02.540 --> 00:23:03.580 line:80%
and killed him with 3 strikes...

00:23:03.580 --> 00:23:04.100 line:80%
What...

00:23:05.450 --> 00:23:07.510 line:80%
She killed Shi Hu with only 3 strikes?

00:23:07.950 --> 00:23:10.390 line:80%
She must be the scion of a famous general!

00:23:11.710 --> 00:23:12.430 line:80%
No.

00:23:12.550 --> 00:23:13.500 line:80%
No?

00:23:14.230 --> 00:23:16.710 line:80%
Then she must be an extraordinary woman
from a common family.

00:23:16.710 --> 00:23:17.710 line:80%
Jiuheng,

00:23:18.020 --> 00:23:20.260 line:80%
you must treat her well.

00:23:21.780 --> 00:23:22.860 line:80%
Now that Shi Hu is dead,

00:23:22.860 --> 00:23:25.820 line:80%
Shi Yue will not let this go for sure.

00:23:25.950 --> 00:23:27.680 line:80%
And Lord Changxin is

00:23:28.190 --> 00:23:30.230 line:80%
determined to take Lucheng.

00:23:30.260 --> 00:23:32.860 line:80%
How do you plan to deal with this?

00:23:34.950 --> 00:23:36.680 line:80%
If I have the Xie Army go all out,

00:23:36.710 --> 00:23:38.060 line:80%
coordinate with He Jingyuan,

00:23:38.060 --> 00:23:39.460 line:80%
and defeat Lord Changxin,

00:23:39.460 --> 00:23:42.390 line:80%
someone else will surely swoop in
to take advantage.

00:23:42.670 --> 00:23:44.100 line:80%
Now, on Wei Yan's side,

00:23:44.220 --> 00:23:45.780 line:80%
in order to cover up the grave error

00:23:45.780 --> 00:23:47.840 line:80%
Wei Xuan committed in the Northwest,

00:23:47.910 --> 00:23:49.440 line:80%
his best option right now is

00:23:50.150 --> 00:23:53.280 line:80%
to steal the credit
for defeating the Chongzhou rebels.

00:23:55.940 --> 00:23:57.470 line:80%
In my opinion,

00:23:57.470 --> 00:23:59.990 line:80%
it's not a bad thing
if he grabs the credit.

00:24:03.050 --> 00:24:04.890 line:80%
Grand Tutor, what do you mean?

00:24:04.920 --> 00:24:06.790 line:80%
Who else in the Great Yin

00:24:06.810 --> 00:24:09.340 line:80%
has been made a marquis at 20?

00:24:09.690 --> 00:24:10.830 line:80%
The moon waxes only to wane;

00:24:10.830 --> 00:24:12.180 line:80%
water brims only to overflow.

00:24:12.180 --> 00:24:14.150 line:80%
Even if you quell the rebellion

00:24:14.180 --> 00:24:15.360 line:80%
and gain military merit,

00:24:15.360 --> 00:24:17.020 line:80%
when you return to the Capital,

00:24:17.020 --> 00:24:19.780 line:80%
what else can His Majesty reward you with?

00:24:20.420 --> 00:24:23.390 line:80%
Given the current treacherous situation
at court,

00:24:23.490 --> 00:24:25.870 line:80%
it is better to step back

00:24:25.890 --> 00:24:30.660 line:80%
and watch others fight desperately
to the death.

00:24:30.890 --> 00:24:32.270 line:80%
You mean,

00:24:32.290 --> 00:24:34.860 line:80%
let the Li family and Wei Yan fight first,

00:24:34.890 --> 00:24:36.660 line:80%
and we will reap the benefits?

00:24:39.640 --> 00:24:41.560 line:80%
Wei Yan holds military power,

00:24:41.580 --> 00:24:44.890 line:80%
and he has He Jingyuan
guarding Jizhou against the enemies.

00:24:44.890 --> 00:24:46.650 line:80%
That is why all these years,

00:24:46.670 --> 00:24:51.640 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li hasn't dared
to openly confront Wei Yan.

00:24:51.720 --> 00:24:53.020 line:80%
Otherwise, Li wouldn't have sent

00:24:53.020 --> 00:24:56.150 line:80%
his heir, his beloved grandson,
Li Huai'an,

00:24:56.180 --> 00:24:57.250 line:80%
to the Northwest

00:24:57.270 --> 00:24:58.750 line:80%
to join the army.

00:24:59.710 --> 00:25:00.950 line:80%
In this case,

00:25:01.210 --> 00:25:02.700 line:80%
Lord Changxin rebelled

00:25:02.720 --> 00:25:05.490 line:80%
to let the military power
fall into the Li family's hands?

00:25:05.490 --> 00:25:07.820 line:80%
The Li family's plot against Lord Changxin

00:25:07.820 --> 00:25:09.820 line:80%
wouldn't go that far.

00:25:09.870 --> 00:25:14.220 line:80%
However, word has it
that Lord Changxin's eldest son,

00:25:14.390 --> 00:25:18.270 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai, has secret dealings
with the Li family frequently.

00:25:18.590 --> 00:25:19.890 line:80%
There's no smoke without fire.

00:25:19.890 --> 00:25:21.280 line:80%
It is very suspicious.

00:25:21.470 --> 00:25:23.100 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai?

00:25:24.090 --> 00:25:26.410 line:80%
I recall some past stories.

00:25:27.540 --> 00:25:30.140 line:80%
After Crown Prince Chengde
and Old General Xie

00:25:30.160 --> 00:25:31.620 line:80%
died in battle in Jinzhou,

00:25:31.770 --> 00:25:33.620 line:80%
the late Emperor suddenly
announced his abdication

00:25:33.050 --> 00:25:34.700 line:80%
[Diligent and Virtuous]

00:25:33.890 --> 00:25:36.300 line:80%
and passed the throne
to the incumbent Emperor,

00:25:36.300 --> 00:25:36.990 line:80%
Qi Sheng.

00:25:38.040 --> 00:25:39.770 line:80%
One day, a fire suddenly broke out
in the Eastern Palace.

00:25:38.660 --> 00:25:40.780 line:80%
[Virtuous and Meritorious]

00:25:40.080 --> 00:25:43.080 line:80%
The Crown Princess and her son
perished in the flames.

00:25:45.340 --> 00:25:47.190 line:80%
At that time, Lord Changxin's wife was

00:25:47.190 --> 00:25:49.610 line:80%
visiting the Eastern Palace
with their eldest son.

00:25:49.610 --> 00:25:51.630 line:80%
Their eldest son was burned
beyond recognition

00:25:51.630 --> 00:25:53.100 line:80%
and couldn't show up in public.

00:25:53.100 --> 00:25:55.540 line:80%
The late Emperor made no compensation.

00:25:56.150 --> 00:25:58.180 line:80%
Lord Changxin has
kept a low profile for years.

00:25:58.180 --> 00:25:59.490 line:80%
He hates the Imperial Court.

00:25:59.490 --> 00:26:01.660 line:80%
This is undeniable.

00:26:02.880 --> 00:26:04.580 line:80%
After going down the mountain,

00:26:04.580 --> 00:26:06.330 line:80%
send a message to the Capital immediately

00:26:06.330 --> 00:26:09.530 line:80%
to secretly investigate
the Eastern Palace's fire case.

00:26:09.820 --> 00:26:11.890 line:80%
Lord Changxin's eldest son, Sui Yuanhuai,

00:26:11.890 --> 00:26:13.690 line:80%
has a trusted aide named Zhao Xun.

00:26:13.690 --> 00:26:16.420 line:80%
He holds the Eastern Palace seal.

00:26:17.900 --> 00:26:19.340 line:80%
Sixteen years ago,

00:26:19.380 --> 00:26:21.310 line:80%
in that fire at the Eastern Palace—

00:26:21.790 --> 00:26:23.590 line:80%
I was one of the lucky survivors.

00:26:24.290 --> 00:26:25.330 line:80%
But now,

00:26:25.370 --> 00:26:28.150 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai has issued a warrant
for his arrest.

00:26:28.490 --> 00:26:30.030 line:80%
We must find Zhao Xun's whereabouts

00:26:30.030 --> 00:26:31.220 line:80%
before he does.

00:26:44.320 --> 00:26:47.030 line:80%
Just now in Little Gongsun's tent,

00:26:47.250 --> 00:26:49.980 line:80%
I couldn't ask much
about your personal affairs.

00:26:50.470 --> 00:26:51.950 line:80%
Now let me ask you.

00:26:51.950 --> 00:26:53.320 line:80%
In this marriage,

00:26:53.340 --> 00:26:55.580 line:80%
did you take a wife or a concubine?

00:26:56.700 --> 00:26:58.340 line:80%
A wife, of course.

00:26:58.580 --> 00:27:00.400 line:80%
Since it is a proper marriage,

00:27:00.430 --> 00:27:02.710 line:80%
why do you look so gloomy?

00:27:09.260 --> 00:27:11.240 line:80%
I hid my identity and deceived her.

00:27:11.750 --> 00:27:12.790 line:80%
Now that she knows

00:27:13.720 --> 00:27:15.560 line:80%
she is marrying the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:27:15.560 --> 00:27:16.960 line:80%
she refuses to accept it.

00:27:17.820 --> 00:27:18.860 line:80%
She said

00:27:19.100 --> 00:27:21.630 line:80%
she never needed military merits
to match me.

00:27:23.110 --> 00:27:25.670 line:80%
She is quite an insightful woman,

00:27:27.500 --> 00:27:30.390 line:80%
very similar to the female disciple

00:27:30.410 --> 00:27:32.160 line:80%
I recently took in at Baxia.

00:27:34.050 --> 00:27:36.390 line:80%
Even if you offered the Marquis of Wu'an
to her in exchange for her husband,

00:27:36.390 --> 00:27:37.670 line:80%
she wouldn't agree.

00:27:38.930 --> 00:27:40.410 line:80%
My wife is also like this.

00:27:40.620 --> 00:27:42.160 line:80%
High office and generous salaries

00:27:42.160 --> 00:27:43.310 line:80%
mean nothing to her.

00:27:43.670 --> 00:27:46.070 line:80%
They are not as worthwhile
as a bowl of rice.

00:27:47.330 --> 00:27:50.000 line:80%
If you give her a few roast chickens,

00:27:50.150 --> 00:27:52.130 line:80%
she'll be happier
than anyone in the world.

00:27:52.130 --> 00:27:54.460 line:80%
She never complains about heavy work

00:27:54.490 --> 00:27:57.430 line:80%
and always has endless energy.

00:27:57.540 --> 00:28:01.630 line:80%
She is always rejoicing
and laughing happily.

00:28:03.430 --> 00:28:04.840 line:80%
Why do I feel like

00:28:04.860 --> 00:28:07.060 line:80%
they are talking about the same person?

00:28:10.540 --> 00:28:11.340 line:80%
Master,

00:28:11.750 --> 00:28:14.060 line:80%
I want to ask you for a favor.

00:28:14.320 --> 00:28:15.120 line:80%
Go ahead.

00:28:15.540 --> 00:28:17.060 line:80%
I implore you, Master,

00:28:17.390 --> 00:28:19.390 line:80%
to take my wife as your goddaughter.

00:28:20.500 --> 00:28:21.780 line:80%
You want to give her

00:28:21.780 --> 00:28:23.820 line:80%
a respectable family background

00:28:24.330 --> 00:28:26.130 line:80%
to silence the gossip?

00:28:27.030 --> 00:28:27.710 line:80%
Yes.

00:28:28.860 --> 00:28:30.590 line:80%
I don't care about her origins.

00:28:31.040 --> 00:28:32.370 line:80%
But I don't want people

00:28:32.470 --> 00:28:34.060 line:80%
to use them as an excuse

00:28:34.060 --> 00:28:35.520 line:80%
to criticize her, either.

00:28:37.320 --> 00:28:38.910 line:80%
What if she's unwilling to accept it

00:28:38.910 --> 00:28:41.540 line:80%
and just wants to be a commoner?

00:28:43.750 --> 00:28:45.210 line:80%
I will respect her choice.

00:28:46.470 --> 00:28:48.920 line:80%
But if she is willing to follow me,

00:28:49.650 --> 00:28:51.510 line:80%
I will never let her suffer again.

00:28:51.990 --> 00:28:53.160 line:80%
I didn't expect

00:28:54.120 --> 00:28:56.120 line:80%
you to be so devoted,

00:28:56.140 --> 00:28:57.810 line:80%
just like your mother.

00:29:01.020 --> 00:29:01.670 line:80%
Alright.

00:29:02.720 --> 00:29:05.290 line:80%
I promise you.

00:29:08.940 --> 00:29:10.540 line:80%
What's the name of the woman

00:29:10.540 --> 00:29:11.990 line:80%
you just married?

00:29:12.350 --> 00:29:13.980 line:80%
And how old is she?

00:29:14.070 --> 00:29:15.870 line:80%
Her name is Fan Changyu.

00:29:15.950 --> 00:29:16.910 line:80%
She is 19.

00:29:19.010 --> 00:29:19.580 line:80%
Your...

00:29:19.960 --> 00:29:21.130 line:80%
Your wife?

00:29:21.970 --> 00:29:22.960 line:80%
Your female disciple?

00:29:22.960 --> 00:29:24.670 line:80%
You are that matrilocal husband?

00:29:24.670 --> 00:29:26.540 line:80%
You were caught to repair the dam?

00:29:29.060 --> 00:29:29.710 line:80%
You...

00:30:09.680 --> 00:30:10.280 line:80%
My Lord...

00:30:13.710 --> 00:30:14.770 line:80%
What's the matter?

00:30:14.780 --> 00:30:16.430 line:80%
It's almost midnight.

00:30:16.460 --> 00:30:17.790 line:80%
I think you should rest.

00:30:19.390 --> 00:30:20.750 line:80%
How is Xie Wu's injury?

00:30:20.750 --> 00:30:22.190 line:80%
The medic said
his internal organs are fine.

00:30:22.190 --> 00:30:23.850 line:80%
He just needs rest to recover.

00:30:24.430 --> 00:30:25.430 line:80%
Glad to hear that.

00:30:27.060 --> 00:30:28.150 line:80%
Bring my horse.

00:30:28.750 --> 00:30:29.420 line:80%
Well, My Lord...

00:30:29.420 --> 00:30:29.940 line:80%
Go.

00:30:31.540 --> 00:30:32.270 line:80%
Yes, My Lord.

00:31:11.140 --> 00:31:13.490 line:80%
[Xie]

00:31:20.150 --> 00:31:22.350 line:80%
Did the marquis order you to guard here?

00:31:22.540 --> 00:31:23.150 line:80%
Yes.

00:31:25.150 --> 00:31:26.410 line:80%
I won't leave the camp.

00:31:27.020 --> 00:31:29.550 line:80%
General, please look after Changning
for me.

00:31:30.540 --> 00:31:31.150 line:80%
Yes.

00:32:28.540 --> 00:32:29.270 line:80%
Who's there?

00:32:29.760 --> 00:32:30.370 line:80%
Come out!

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:35.580 line:80%
It's me.

00:32:40.100 --> 00:32:41.300 line:80%
What brings you here?

00:32:42.710 --> 00:32:44.040 line:80%
I couldn't fall asleep,

00:32:44.360 --> 00:32:45.960 line:80%
so I came out to clear my head.

00:32:47.370 --> 00:32:48.700 line:80%
You can't sleep either?

00:32:50.650 --> 00:32:53.180 line:80%
I saw too many dead bodies
on the battlefield.

00:32:54.410 --> 00:32:56.070 line:80%
It weighs heavily on my heart.

00:33:04.620 --> 00:33:06.350 line:80%
The first time I went to battle,

00:33:08.750 --> 00:33:10.410 line:80%
I couldn't fall asleep either

00:33:11.260 --> 00:33:12.920 line:80%
and had nightmares all night.

00:33:14.410 --> 00:33:15.690 line:80%
But the second time,

00:33:16.030 --> 00:33:18.290 line:80%
I killed even more people than the first.

00:33:20.230 --> 00:33:21.310 line:80%
I couldn't sleep

00:33:22.260 --> 00:33:23.520 line:80%
at all the whole night.

00:33:25.670 --> 00:33:28.070 line:80%
So I went out
and found a random place to fish

00:33:29.150 --> 00:33:30.470 line:80%
for the entire night

00:33:30.880 --> 00:33:32.330 line:80%
until I was exhausted.

00:33:33.840 --> 00:33:36.240 line:80%
Then I went back
and fell asleep right away.

00:33:37.500 --> 00:33:38.540 line:80%
Since then,

00:33:39.410 --> 00:33:41.270 line:80%
I've never had a nightmare again.

00:33:47.150 --> 00:33:48.280 line:80%
It's all in the past.

00:34:02.780 --> 00:34:04.640 line:80%
If you're still feeling stifled,

00:34:04.910 --> 00:34:05.840 line:80%
let's spar a bit.

00:34:09.640 --> 00:34:10.189 line:80%
What?

00:34:10.650 --> 00:34:11.200 line:80%
Scared?

00:34:15.650 --> 00:34:16.380 line:80%
Let's do it.

00:34:40.100 --> 00:34:41.150 line:80%
What was that?

00:34:41.249 --> 00:34:42.430 line:80%
Biting the hand that fed you?

00:34:42.430 --> 00:34:43.840 line:80%
All is fair in war.

00:34:44.810 --> 00:34:46.400 line:80%
That actually makes sense.

00:34:47.310 --> 00:34:49.150 line:80%
You weren't fighting seriously.

00:34:49.150 --> 00:34:51.420 line:80%
On the battlefield, I couldn't beat you.

00:34:51.450 --> 00:34:53.510 line:80%
Close combat relies mostly on speed.

00:34:53.979 --> 00:34:55.150 line:80%
You're good with short blades,

00:34:55.150 --> 00:34:57.150 line:80%
but your moves are heavy and powerful.

00:34:57.150 --> 00:34:58.260 line:80%
Use less brute force,

00:34:58.260 --> 00:34:59.190 line:80%
go with the flow,

00:34:59.190 --> 00:35:00.250 line:80%
and use more finesse

00:35:00.250 --> 00:35:01.450 line:80%
to pick up your speed.

00:35:03.610 --> 00:35:04.230 line:80%
Let me try again.

00:35:04.230 --> 00:35:04.720 line:80%
Come on.

00:35:26.850 --> 00:35:28.560 line:80%
You were holding back just now?

00:35:28.560 --> 00:35:29.570 line:80%
I'm not stupid.

00:35:30.070 --> 00:35:32.270 line:80%
I've got to figure out your style first.

00:35:33.420 --> 00:35:34.280 line:80%
One more round.

00:35:39.870 --> 00:35:42.200 line:80%
Here, this is ready. Be careful. It's hot.

00:35:53.600 --> 00:35:54.440 line:80%
It's so good.

00:35:54.900 --> 00:35:56.230 line:80%
It tastes sweet and sour.

00:35:56.230 --> 00:35:57.630 line:80%
Did you bring seasoning?

00:35:58.460 --> 00:35:58.980 line:80%
No.

00:35:59.730 --> 00:36:00.930 line:80%
I picked some fruits.

00:36:01.310 --> 00:36:03.180 line:80%
Some are sour, some are spicy.

00:36:04.630 --> 00:36:06.090 line:80%
You tasted them one by one?

00:36:18.070 --> 00:36:19.670 line:80%
What's wrong? Is it bad?

00:36:28.420 --> 00:36:29.840 line:80%
Don't be so nice to me.

00:36:31.250 --> 00:36:32.850 line:80%
You are the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:36:34.160 --> 00:36:36.420 line:80%
And I'm just an ordinary female butcher.

00:36:36.920 --> 00:36:38.720 line:80%
You are the best woman in my eyes.

00:36:39.460 --> 00:36:40.750 line:80%
I'm just into you.

00:36:42.860 --> 00:36:44.190 line:80%
Don't be into me.

00:36:46.560 --> 00:36:49.560 line:80%
You should find a wife
whose background matches yours

00:36:50.190 --> 00:36:51.590 line:80%
and live a glorious life,

00:36:52.250 --> 00:36:54.030 line:80%
admired by thousands.

00:36:59.100 --> 00:37:00.310 line:80%
Admired by others?

00:37:02.420 --> 00:37:04.150 line:80%
I, Xie Zheng, got where I am today

00:37:04.150 --> 00:37:05.610 line:80%
through military merits,

00:37:05.710 --> 00:37:07.110 line:80%
not by their admiration.

00:37:09.220 --> 00:37:10.620 line:80%
I am the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:37:10.730 --> 00:37:11.970 line:80%
If I have to fear

00:37:12.320 --> 00:37:14.440 line:80%
the world's judgment
when choosing my wife,

00:37:14.440 --> 00:37:16.170 line:80%
wouldn't that be too pathetic?

00:37:19.550 --> 00:37:20.590 line:80%
In the past,

00:37:21.650 --> 00:37:23.650 line:80%
I never thought of getting married.

00:37:25.110 --> 00:37:26.710 line:80%
Being ruthless like my uncle

00:37:27.150 --> 00:37:29.150 line:80%
or being devoted like my mother were

00:37:29.150 --> 00:37:30.410 line:80%
neither what I wanted.

00:37:31.670 --> 00:37:32.820 line:80%
I was born on the battlefield,

00:37:32.820 --> 00:37:34.390 line:80%
and I'll die on the battlefield.

00:37:34.390 --> 00:37:35.780 line:80%
I thought my life was

00:37:36.850 --> 00:37:38.160 line:80%
bound to end in battle.

00:37:40.110 --> 00:37:40.900 line:80%
So,

00:37:42.280 --> 00:37:44.740 line:80%
I didn't want a woman
to remain a widow for me.

00:37:47.260 --> 00:37:48.710 line:80%
But after meeting you,

00:37:49.460 --> 00:37:50.660 line:80%
I've actually become

00:37:52.640 --> 00:37:54.040 line:80%
a little afraid of death.

00:38:08.070 --> 00:38:08.630 line:80%
Alright,

00:38:09.380 --> 00:38:10.580 line:80%
let's talk about you.

00:38:11.040 --> 00:38:12.830 line:80%
When all this is over,

00:38:13.030 --> 00:38:14.230 line:80%
what do you want to do?

00:38:15.000 --> 00:38:17.380 line:80%
Still want to raise 100 pigs

00:38:17.380 --> 00:38:18.580 line:80%
and butcher 100 pigs?

00:38:21.750 --> 00:38:23.210 line:80%
The future is too far away.

00:38:24.340 --> 00:38:26.270 line:80%
I can only think about the present.

00:38:27.380 --> 00:38:28.630 line:80%
I promised Changning

00:38:28.850 --> 00:38:30.330 line:80%
I'd find Qian and Bao'er.

00:38:31.510 --> 00:38:32.900 line:80%
Also, Mr. Zhao,

00:38:32.900 --> 00:38:34.300 line:80%
Jin Yuanbao and his crew,

00:38:35.340 --> 00:38:39.070 line:80%
and all the other fellow villagers of mine
scattered all over the land,

00:38:39.070 --> 00:38:40.470 line:80%
I want to bring them home.

00:38:41.900 --> 00:38:43.630 line:80%
Although Lin'an is destroyed,

00:38:44.740 --> 00:38:46.550 line:80%
we can rebuild it

00:38:47.680 --> 00:38:50.240 line:80%
with our own hands, brick by brick.

00:38:52.510 --> 00:38:53.150 line:80%
Alright.

00:38:54.080 --> 00:38:55.950 line:80%
When everything is over,

00:38:56.700 --> 00:38:58.960 line:80%
I will petition to govern the Northwest.

00:38:59.040 --> 00:38:59.950 line:80%
That way,

00:39:00.150 --> 00:39:03.190 line:80%
whatever happens in the Capital
won't concern me anymore.

00:39:03.190 --> 00:39:05.680 line:80%
I'll rebuild Lin'an with you.

00:39:05.850 --> 00:39:06.980 line:80%
How does that sound?

00:39:10.530 --> 00:39:11.540 line:80%
You are willing

00:39:13.620 --> 00:39:14.660 line:80%
to stay in Lin'an?

00:39:18.100 --> 00:39:20.230 line:80%
The days I spent with you in Lin'an were

00:39:20.840 --> 00:39:22.010 line:80%
the happiest time

00:39:22.500 --> 00:39:23.750 line:80%
in my life.

00:39:25.910 --> 00:39:28.510 line:80%
Brother-in-Law, Mrs. Zhao
asked you to go there for lunch.

00:39:28.510 --> 00:39:31.710 line:80%
Woke up every morning to the sound
of you butchering pigs.

00:39:34.020 --> 00:39:36.400 line:80%
Spent time with Changning and Mr. Zhao,

00:39:36.600 --> 00:39:37.840 line:80%
playing chess

00:39:37.870 --> 00:39:39.130 line:80%
and building snowmen.

00:39:40.870 --> 00:39:41.910 line:80%
At noon,

00:39:41.950 --> 00:39:44.880 line:80%
I could eat the noodles
with pork intestine you made.

00:39:45.210 --> 00:39:49.000 line:80%
and listen to Mrs. Zhao
talk about all the village gossip.

00:39:49.070 --> 00:39:50.360 line:80%
Thirty taels?

00:39:52.260 --> 00:39:54.280 line:80%
Look who's here.

00:39:54.380 --> 00:39:56.660 line:80%
At night, you and I

00:39:57.800 --> 00:40:01.400 line:80%
listened to the sound of insects chirping
and studied together.

00:40:02.120 --> 00:40:03.270 line:80%
I miss

00:40:06.150 --> 00:40:07.380 line:80%
all of it so much.

00:40:27.260 --> 00:40:28.660 line:80%
You're gripping so hard.

00:40:29.230 --> 00:40:31.760 line:80%
Aren't you afraid
your hand will bleed again?

00:40:33.180 --> 00:40:34.840 line:80%
I'm more afraid you'll hit me.

00:40:35.070 --> 00:40:37.290 line:80%
That's because you kissed me randomly.

00:40:38.140 --> 00:40:39.200 line:80%
If you don't hit me,

00:40:39.410 --> 00:40:41.210 line:80%
I won't kiss you randomly again.

00:40:44.820 --> 00:40:45.550 line:80%
Eat up.